## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="362dd-102"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> 类是抽象 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> 类的具体实现。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-102">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class is a concrete implementation of the abstract <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> class.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="362dd-103"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类类似于 ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> 类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-103">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class is similar to the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-104"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>如果你使用了 ASP.NET 类，则类有许多用于访问缓存的属性和方法 <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-104">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has many properties and methods for accessing the cache that will be familiar to you if you have used the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-105">和类之间的主要区别在于， <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> 该类已 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> 更改，.NET Framework 不是 ASP.NET 应用程序的应用程序可以使用它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-105">The main differences between the <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> and <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classes are that the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has been changed to make it usable by .NET Framework applications that are not ASP.NET applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-106">例如，类对 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> 程序集没有依赖项 `System.Web` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-106">For example, the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has no dependencies on the `System.Web` assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-107">另一差别在于，您可以创建类的多个实例， <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> 以便在同一个应用程序和同一个实例中使用 <xref:System.AppDomain> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-107">Another difference is that you can create multiple instances of the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class for use in the same application and in the same <xref:System.AppDomain> instance.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="362dd-108"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>类不允许 `null` 作为缓存中的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-108">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class does not allow `null` as a value in the cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-109">任何添加或更改值为的缓存条目的尝试 `null` 都将失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-109">Any attempt to add or change a cache entry with a value of `null` will fail.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="362dd-110">该 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> 类型不实现 *缓存区域*。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-110">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> type does not implement *cache regions*.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-111">因此，在调用 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> 实现包含区域参数的基方法的方法时，不要传递参数的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-111">Therefore, when you call <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> methods that implement base methods that contain a parameter for regions, do not pass a value for the parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-112">使用 region 参数的方法均提供默认 `null` 值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-112">The methods that use the region parameter all supply a default `null` value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-113">例如， <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache.AddOrGetExisting%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 方法重载具有一个参数， `regionName` 其默认值为 `null` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-113">For example, the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache.AddOrGetExisting%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method overload has a `regionName` parameter whose default value is `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="362dd-114">下面的示例声明对默认内存缓存实例的引用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-114">The following example declares a reference to the default memory cache instance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-115">缓存项使用 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.CacheItemPolicy> 对象来提供该缓存项的逐出和过期详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-115">The cache entry uses a <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.CacheItemPolicy> object to provide eviction and expiration details for the cache entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="362dd-116">它还使用 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ChangeMonitor> 对象来监视源数据的状态， (是文件系统上的文件) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="362dd-116">It also uses a <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ChangeMonitor> object to monitor the state of the source data (which is a file) on the file system.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Private Sub btnGet_Click(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As EventArgs)   
    Dim cache As ObjectCache = MemoryCache.[Default]   
    Dim fileContents As String = TryCast(cache("filecontents"), String)   
  
    If fileContents Is Nothing Then   
        Dim policy As New CacheItemPolicy()   
        Dim filePaths As New List(Of String)()   
        filePaths.Add("c:\cache\example.txt")   
  
        policy.ChangeMonitors.Add(New HostFileChangeMonitor(filePaths))   
  
        ' Fetch the file contents.  
        fileContents = File.ReadAllText("c:\cache\example.txt")   
  
        cache.[Set]("filecontents", fileContents, policy)   
    End If   
  
    Label1.Text = fileContents  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void btnGet_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)  
{  
    ObjectCache cache = MemoryCache.Default;  
    string fileContents = cache["filecontents"] as string;  
  
    if (fileContents == null)  
    {  
        CacheItemPolicy policy = new CacheItemPolicy();  
  
        List<string> filePaths = new List<string>();  
        filePaths.Add("c:\\cache\\example.txt");  
  
        policy.ChangeMonitors.Add(new   
        HostFileChangeMonitor(filePaths));  
  
        // Fetch the file contents.  
        fileContents =   
            File.ReadAllText("c:\\cache\\example.txt");  
  
        cache.Set("filecontents", fileContents, policy);  
    }  
  
    Label1.Text = fileContents;  
}  
```
